name: Appeals Note Chapter repealed June 30, 2009.  L 2004, c 141, 7. L 2004, c 141, 5 provides:
text: Appeals.  From the order made on an application for reconsideration or rehearing by the public utilities commission under this chapter, an appeal shall lie in the manner provided in section 269-15.5. [L 2004, c 141, pt of §1]
